				<p>
					Fast Food Guides is an <strong>independent publication</strong> and is not affiliated
					with, endorsed by, sponsored by, or officially connected to any fast food corporation,
					restaurant chain, franchise organization, or food service company. Any references to
					specific brands, restaurants, or menu items are made solely for informational and
