				</p>

				<h2>7. User Conduct</h2>
				<p>By using this Site, you agree not to:</p>
				<ul>
					<li>Use the Site for any unlawful purpose or in violation of any applicable laws or regulations</li>
					<li>Reproduce, duplicate, or copy any content from the Site for commercial purposes without authorization</li>
